desc: A mutt is any dog that is a little bit rebellious, lives life to the full, and loves adventure. At Outback Mutts we want to help you give your mutt a full and happy life. We make sustainable, biodegradable and durable pet bags, bowls and other products. Our up-cycled Rescued Collars are unique, stylish and loved.

layout.text: To inspire moments of fun and adventure for all mutts through our brand and actions.
